============ 7segment-avr ============

       ---    ---    ---    ---
      |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |
       ---    ---    ---    ---
      |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |
       ---    ---    ---    ---        


a (little) library for using 7-segment
displays in avr microcontrollers using
avr libc.

tested on atmega328p (arduino uno).
